no matter how small.

442
00:31:46,104 --> 00:31:50,144
You just crossed the line, Horton,
and I'm gonna make you pay.

443
00:31:57,182 --> 00:31:58,642
That Horton is a menace.

444
00:31:58,917 --> 00:32:01,347
He has those kids using
their imaginations.

445
00:32:01,753 --> 00:32:02,513
It's sick.

446
00:32:03,054 --> 00:32:06,864
All right, gotta get this speck
up to the top of Mount Nool, ASAP,

447
00:32:07,492 --> 00:32:11,622
